Description:
    Launch qemu virtual machines.

Usage: xl-virt <Option>

Configuration:
    Derived from ~/.config/xlotus/xlotus.cfg:
        virt_drive_dir : directory of qemu raw drives.
        virt_iso_dir : directory of iso files.

Option: One of the following:

    -h , --help:
        Print this help page.

    -m , --mkdrive:
        Make a new raw drive in virt_drive_dir.

    -i , --iso:
        Boot from a drive in virt_drive_dir and
        an iso in virt_iso_dir.

    -d , --drive:
        Boot from a drive in virt_drive_dir.
